Both are &quot;description&quot; languages but help neither developers nor  
client apps completely.

For RESTful apps, documenting link relations, URIs (in cases where  
hypermedia does not help), URI templates or equivalent, media types,  
formats, methods supported etc in prose works best.

Subbu

